    <item>
      <title>特朗普2.0时代，银行家们重拾交易愿望清单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/bankers-dust-off-dealmaking-wish-lists-under-trump-2-0-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的米歇尔·戴维斯表示，唐纳德·特朗普第二届政府放松反垄断监管的前景，让华尔街交易员感到乐观。她在“彭博未平仓合约”上表示，并购交易似乎更有可能继续进行——除了一些跨境交易。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/bankers-dust-off-dealmaking-wish-lists-under-trump-2-0-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 16:10:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全文：英国央行贝利谈降息、英国预算、美国关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/in-full-boe-s-bailey-on-rate-cut-uk-budget-us-tariffs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利讨论了央行决定将基准利率下调至 4.75%、市场对财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯上周预算案的反应，以及唐纳德·特朗普连任后美国关税可能对英国经济产生的影响。他在伦敦接受了彭博社记者弗朗辛·拉夸的采访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/in-full-boe-s-bailey-on-rate-cut-uk-budget-us-tariffs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 16:05:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨拒绝下周进行信任投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/scholz-rejects-opposition-s-call-for-confidence-vote-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨拒绝了保守派反对党领袖弗里德里希·默茨的要求，即他应在下周初举行信任投票，为最早于 1 月中旬举行的选举铺平道路。朔尔茨试图将选举推迟到 3 月。查德·托马斯在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/scholz-rejects-opposition-s-call-for-confidence-vote-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:51:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥储蓄减少资本支出，TC Energy 股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/tc-energy-trp-shares-rise-as-mexico-savings-reduce-capital-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TC Energy Corp. 的股价上涨至四年多来的最高水平，因为这家加拿大管道公司由于墨西哥管道项目的节省而降低了资本支出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/tc-energy-trp-shares-rise-as-mexico-savings-reduce-capital-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:47:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自特朗普获胜以来，与俄罗斯相关的股票在附近市场飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/russia-linked-stocks-surge-on-nearby-markets-since-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管仍存在巨大障碍，但唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利促使投资者为解决乌克兰战争做好准备，从土耳其到东欧，受俄罗斯影响的股票纷纷上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/russia-linked-stocks-surge-on-nearby-markets-since-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:29:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利 Mol 因与俄罗斯达成石油协议而获得强劲现金流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/hungary-refiner-mol-sees-strong-cash-flow-after-russian-oil-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利能源公司 Mol Nyrt. 在调整了通过乌克兰管道运输俄罗斯原油的交易后，预计即使欧洲炼油商面临严峻的市场环境，现金流仍将为正。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/hungary-refiner-mol-sees-strong-cash-flow-after-russian-oil-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:09:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行称冲击英国政府债券市场的交易平仓可能已经结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/boe-says-unwind-of-trades-that-rocked-gilt-market-is-likely-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行官员表示，上周预算公布后英国债券的抛售因投资者的配置而加剧，这表明他们认为最糟糕的下滑时期已经过去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/boe-says-unwind-of-trades-that-rocked-gilt-market-is-likely-over</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 14:44:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对德国债务狂潮的担忧首次成为关键市场指标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/fear-of-german-debt-binge-flips-key-market-gauge-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在德国政府中财政保守派的领袖被解职后，交易员们为德国可能出售更多债券做好了准备，这导致一些市场人士开始考虑一个可能对更高债务更加容忍的新政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/fear-of-german-debt-binge-flips-key-market-gauge-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 09:31:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
